  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nIt seems that the Nethermind node sometimes estimates incorrect gas values.\r\nWhen we execute the attached test case, the node produces 45811.\r\nWe think that the correct output is 43511.\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nSteps to reproduce the behavior:\r\n1. Download test files\r\n[test_cases.zip](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/9292786/test_cases.zip)\r\n\r\n2. Run the node with the following command\r\n    Nethermind.Runner --config ./test_cases/nethermind.cfg\r\n\r\n3. Execute the javascript test case\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n43511\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Linux\r\n - Version : Nethermind/v1.13.6-0-be7b4ab4c-20220808/X64-Linux/6.0.7",
