    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Just wanted to add to this issue, as we are seeing similar things.\r\n\r\nFor example, this `eth_estimateGas` call:\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"method\": \"eth_estimateGas\",\r\n  \"params\": [\r\n    {\r\n      \"data\": \"\",\r\n      \"from\": \"0xa21740833858985e4d801533a808786d3647fb83\",\r\n      \"to\": \"0x9008d19f58aabd9ed0d60971565aa8510560ab41\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"0xede586\"\r\n  ],\r\n  \"id\": 3748644\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nWith Nethermind returns:\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"result\": \"0x23102\",\r\n  \"id\": 3748644\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever, other nodes we've tested (Geth, ~~Erigon~~, Tenderly) return:\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"id\": 3748644,\r\n  \"result\": \"0x216d5\"\r\n}\r\n```",
